The paper deals with complexity classes and their relationships, which suggests that it belongs to cs.CC (Computational Complexity). The paper also discusses set theory and graph theory, which are common topics in cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) and cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory), respectively. The use of logical operators and proofs suggests that the paper may also belong to cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) and cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics).
